Privacy Policy

This community is operated by Commonshub in partnership with the [CREATOR / SHOW NAME] team.

We are committed to minimal data collection and transparent operation.

1. What We Collect  
When you create an account, we store:
- The information you provide (username, email, profile details)
- Your posts and media
- Basic technical logs necessary to operate the service

2. How Your Data Is Used  
Your data is used only to:
- Provide and maintain the service
- Enable federation with other servers
- Support moderation and community safety
- Prevent abuse and spam

We do not sell your data.  
We do not run advertising.  
We do not use behavioral tracking.

3. Public Content  
Public posts are publicly accessible and may be copied, indexed, or shared by other servers in the Fediverse.

4. Media Storage & Backups  
Media and posts may be stored and backed up on infrastructure used to operate this service.

5. Federation  
Because this is a federated service:
- Content may be delivered to other servers
- Content from other servers may appear here

Servers that present safety or policy risks may be blocked.

6. Data Retention  
If you delete your account, your profile data will be removed.  
Some content may remain in backups or on federated servers.

7. Cookies & Analytics  
Only essential technical functions are used to keep the service running.  
No advertising or cross-site tracking is used.

8. Service Hosting  
This service is hosted in:  
[HOSTING COUNTRY]

9. Contact  
For privacy questions or data requests, contact:  
[ADMIN EMAIL]
